## Task Breakdown for the Airflow DAG

|                      Task Name                     |                                                       Description                                                      |         Stored data         | GETDATE Marker | Parallelizable? |
| :------------------------------------------------: | :--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------: | :-------------------------: | :------------: | :-------------: |
| **task\_\_process\_transpariz\_delete\_alpha\_ma** |        Filter staging rows with `strReportPortfHoldSrc` ∈ {ALP, MA}, delete matching entries from target table.        | `df_keys` from ALP/MA scope |        -       |  Yes (by chunk) |
|    **task\_\_process\_transpariz\_delete\_dmc**    |           Filter staging rows with `strReportPortfHoldSrc` = DMC, delete matching entries from target table.           |   `df_keys` from DMC scope  |        -       |  Yes (by chunk) |
|     **task\_\_insert\_final\_processed\_data**     | Filter `df_updated` on `numLowestInventoryflag == 1`, map to ORM objects (applying defaults), bulk‑insert into target. |              -              |        -       |       Yes       |

